at the climax of lucian of samosata 's necyomantia , tiresias in hades is asked " what is the best way of life ? " to which he responds , " the life of the ordinary guy : forget philosophers and their metaphysics . "   the breasts of tiresias ( ) is a surrealist play by guillaume apollinaire written in 1903 .

